{"tid":1295234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[建制變天］田北俊與三自由黨榮譽主席要求張宇人辭去行會成員","createTime":"2019-07-08T03:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T09:01:40.000Z","uid":174295,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"bd7f9c5e71a15653aeee44653f151727484ff947","tid":1295234,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:15:01.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】自由黨榮譽主席田北俊認為，自由黨在6月9日反修訂逃犯條例遊行後即時發聲明支持政府，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">猶如做了幫兇</span></strong>，他與另外三名自由黨榮譽主席要求現任主席張宇人辭去行政會議成員一職。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，據他了解，自由黨黨魁兼立法會議員鍾國斌當時未有簽署自由黨支持政府修例的聲明。"},{"pid":"daa4c3665dd6ee70107517e69b0e533e12491280","tid":1295234,"uid":75664,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:16:21.000Z","msg":"田少落好注未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6726838deb206ed8ba38f01592495112e5ddaab","tid":1295234,"uid":84633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:21:49.000Z","msg":"又反了！"},{"pid":"c9015437c3737b3e109ad976122140ab14b8da0b","tid":1295234,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5ec7d2cc54ac8897cc435eedfa3566dfa3ab98","tid":1295234,"uid":94739,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"daa4c3665dd6ee70107517e69b0e533e12491280","tid":1295234,"uid":75664,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:16:21.000Z","msg":"田少落好注未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:44:15.000Z","msg":"買定離手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b9a41b407827e5aca9ad911fe0f8d374f8c787","tid":1295234,"uid":43061,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:44:37.000Z","msg":"睇得出家下個政府搞唔撚掂呢壇野"},{"pid":"3e56b9a8c874b7cfc0492ec9fd5b0f4076c